  "title": "Project Enginner(RC Work)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Work together with drafter to submit the shop drawing.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate on the PE design issues. </li>\n  <li>Liaise with professional staff such as architects and engineers.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and inspect all work undertaken by contractors to ensure structural soundness.</li>\n  <li>Project materials submission. </li>\n  <li>Coordinate site work arrangment and planing. </li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements: </p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/Deploma in civil or structural engineering (essential).</li>\n  <li>6 years of work experience as a structural engineer (essential).</li>\n  <li>Experience in project management.</li>\n  <li>Advanced knowledge of construction methods, materials, and legal regulations.</li>\n</ul>",
